A middle-aged Asian man in business casual attire stands at a crossroads in a lush tropical garden, one path lined with deep blue lotus flowers, the other with bright orange marigolds. He faces the orange path with confident posture, a small backpack slung over one shoulder. Behind him, the Singapore skyline rises through morning mist. The scene is rendered in the soft, dreamy watercolor style of Studio Ghibli, with dappled sunlight filtering through frangipani trees, gentle wind rustling leaves, and a sense of hopeful new beginnings. Warm golden hour lighting bathes everything in optimism. Small details like a butterfly taking flight and distant clouds shaped like stepping stones add whimsy to this moment of professional transformation.
